Description: A crowd-based hiring platform for startups, small and medium size companies based out of United States. Crowmsp.com
Headquarters Regions: Greater Houston Area, Southern US
Full Description: CrowdMSP is one of the fastest growing crowd recruiting platform that enables employers to post hundreds of jobs free on the platform and employers pay only when they hire through us. CrowdMSP is a technology enabled platform that enables you to manage entire recruitment process through well designed and excellent screening process through which we deliver talent at the shortest time possible. At CrowdMSP, we work closely with our clients from the time they sign up for our services and post job orders and until that job order is closed through us. We are currently serving in both IT & Non IT industries at all level to fill out the positions and bridge the gaps between talent and employers through crowd recruiting approach.  HOW IT WORKS: In order for you to work with us as a verified employer, you need to sign up a small agreement between hiring company and CrowdMSP. A Memorandum of agreement will be signed agreeing on the terms of services and payment on the jobs closed by CrowdMSP. As soon as we finish up this paper work we will create your employer log in to our platform where in you can create branded jobs of your company on our platform as may jobs you want. After publishing the jobs our technology enabled platform will identify the description of the job and select recruitment professionals who are associated with CrowdMSP to find talent for the positions open with our clients. Based on the position, location, industry and type of job the work order will be assigned to those recruiters who have relevant experience finding the talent in that industry and domain. As soon as our crowd receives the position based on their expertise they start hunting the talent, in order to make quality of talent to our employers CrowdMSP’s account manager will be working as a mediator to screen and filter the best of the best profiles to our employers so that employers doesn’t have to go through the process of screening resumes by spending lot of time. Once we submit screened and get to go candidates through our technology enabled platform to employers they can log in to check the profiles and take it for other round of interviews. In true sense CrowdMSP’s account managers works as a consultant with their expertise and knowledge in the industry they attract, engage and send you qualified talent pool for closing your job orders.

Switzerland’s Matterhorn represents what Matterhorn Consulting is all about…getting to your business or career summit. Matterhorn Consulting is uniquely positioned to help manufacturers, distributors, security dealers-integrators, and end users work more effectively in the changing security industry. We believe training is a process, not a one-time event. Participants will benefit by being able to apply what was learned to their work; gain practical tools to leverage the learning experience; learn from “lessons learned” and shared from different perspectives; and engage in dynamic classroom experiences!
